Detail description of this web-Application
This is multimedia web application in which user can upload his media(music,videos,images) and have private media and user has an option 
to directly embed the media from facebook,youtube,soundcloud and has a profile which specifies latest updates and recent activities of 
user's friends.
SECURITY:
activation of the account(creating all userdata) is only possible after the confirmation of link sent in the mail of the user.
all the passwords are encrypted(oneway).
all the ins and outs for the web-application are restricted with out a valid user-id
User have an option to have access to media with password reconfirmation.
Improved post  methods to transfer data.

Yet to come features:
-User can also customize his own profile page with his own background picture,patterns,etc(like in gmail).
-user and his particular friend can have a common media section where they can upload media and only they can have access.
-adding a notifications pop-up
-If the password is incorrect for more than three times and failed to activate through confirmation link.all the user data will be deleted 
and saved in secured way with the specific id and the id is sent through mail and he can retrieve all the data by entering the id and his 
own password. 
